[6.0, "o", "\u001b[2J\u001b[H                                                         \u2502 repo     ananta\n                                                         \u2502 cwd      .\n                                                         \u2502 git      Krusty  main \u2713\n                                                         \u2502 hub      \u25cf localhost:5000\n                                                         \u2502 auth     session_env\n                                                         \u2502 section  help\n                                                         \u2502 mode     normal\n                                                         \u2502 \n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n[NAV]                  |  HELP                                  |  DETAIL                           \n>. Dashboard           |                                        |                                   \n . Goals               | j selection_down Move selection down   |   Commands:                       \n . Tasks               | k selection_up Move selection up       |     :section <id>   switch section\n . Artifacts           | h focus_left Move focus left           |     :refresh        reload data   \n . Knowledge           | l focus_right Move focus right         |     :focus <pane>   nav/content...\n . Config              | gg selection_first Move to first item  |     :help           keybindings   \n . Templates           | G selection_last Move to last item     |                                   \n . System              | / search Open search                   |                                   \n . Audit               | : command_mode Open command line       |  CHAT                             \n . Terminal            | r refresh Refresh active section       |   ACTIVE: #room                   \n . Share / Teilnehmer  | ? help Toggle help overlay             |   [#room] AI notes                \n*. Help                | enter inspect Inspect selected item    |   ------------------------------  \n                       | q quit Quit operator TUI               |   keine Nachrichten               \n                       |                                        |   ------------------------------  \n                       |                                        |   Ctrl+E Eingabe  Ctrl+W Kanal    \n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nendpoint=http://localhost:5000 auth=session_env focus=navigation mode=normal ready VAI:off\n \nCommands: :refresh :section <id>  [Ctrl+W] Focus/Kanal  [Ctrl+J/Ctrl+K] Move  [Ctrl+R] Refresh  [...\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nHELP\nj selection_down Move selection down\nk selection_up Move selection up\nh focus_left Move focus left\nl focus_right Move focus right\ngg selection_first Move to first item\nG selection_last Move to last item\n/ search Open search\n: command_mode Open command line\nr refresh Refresh active section\n? help Toggle help overlay\nenter inspect Inspect selected item\nq quit Quit operator TUI\n"]
